OL,7,FTwo teachers and a pupil were hurt in
OL,8,Fthe incident but have now been
OL,9,Freleased from hospital.
OL,11,FA 13-year-old girl has now been
OL,12,Fcharged with three counts of attempted
OL,13,Fmurder, Superintendent Ross Evans, of
OL,14,FDyfed-Powys Police, said.
OL,16,FA 15-year-old boy was arrested later
OL,17,Fon Wednesday after police received
OL,18,Freports about messages on social media
OL,19,Freferring to the stabbing.
OL,21,FHe remains in custody, Mr Evans said.
