OL,7,F"The Crown Prosecution Service has
OL,8,Fauthorised Dyfed Powys Police to
OL,9,Fcharge a girl in connection with the
OL,10,Fstabbing of three people at Ysgol
OL,11,FDyffryn Amman yesterday.
OL,13,F"The youth has been remanded in
OL,14,Fcustody to appear before Llanelli
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court tomorrow on Friday,
OL,16,F26 April 2024.
OL,18,F"Criminal proceedings are active, and
OL,19,Fthe defendant has the right to a fair
OL,20,Ftrial.
